---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for CLI Tools Guide — how we handle data, cookies, and ads.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-6 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">Home</a></li>
        <li><span class="mx-1">›</span></li>
        <li class="text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose-tool">
      <p>CLI Tools Guide respects your privacy. This page explains what data is collected, why it is used, and how to contact us about privacy concerns.</p>

      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>No user accounts are required. The site collects anonymous analytics data (page views, referrers, browser and device information) to improve content and performance.</p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>Ads on this site are served by Google AdSense. Google may use cookies, device identifiers, and similar technologies to deliver ads, personalize ads, and measure ad performance. We do not control Google’s data collection and processing practices.</p>
      <p>For more information, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's advertising policies</a> and <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2>Advertising Choices</h2>
      <p>You can manage your ad preferences and opt out of personalized advertising via <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a>. To opt out of Google Analytics across websites, install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p>

      <h2>Google Services</h2>
      <p>This site may use Google Analytics and Google AdSense. Google may collect information about your use of this site. To opt out of Google Analytics across websites, install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>. To control ad personalization from Google, visit <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a>.</p>

      <h2>Cookies &amp; Tracking</h2>
      <p>Cookies and similar technologies are used by both this site and third parties for analytics and advertising. You can manage or block cookies in your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>This site links to external resources (GitHub, official docs). External sites have their own privacy policies; this site is not responsible for their content or practices.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention &amp; Rights</h2>
      <p>Data collected for analytics is retained by the respective third-party providers according to their policies. If you have questions about data we control, contact us and we will respond to reasonable requests to update or remove personal information where applicable.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about privacy? Email <a href="mailto:lucky071118@gmail.com">lucky071118@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

